      "sentences": [
        {"en": "What do you do at Christmas?", "zh": "你圣诞节做什么?"},
        {"en": "We give cards and presents.", "zh": "我们送贺卡和礼物。"},
        {"en": "Do you like Spring Festival?", "zh": "你喜欢春节吗?"},
        {"en": "Yes, we get lucky money.", "zh": "是的, 我们收压岁钱。"},
        {"en": "People eat mooncakes at Mid-Autumn Festival.", "zh": "人们在中秋节吃月饼。"},
        {"en": "They watch fireworks at New Year.", "zh": "他们在新年看烟花。"}
