        {"en": "Robots will help us do housework.", "zh": "机器人将帮我们做家务。"},
        {"en": "Will people travel to Mars?", "zh": "人们会去火星旅行吗?"},
        {"en": "Maybe we'll have flying cars.", "zh": "也许我们将有飞行汽车。"},
        {"en": "There won't be any pollution.", "zh": "将不会有任何污染。"},
        {"en": "When I grow up, I want to be a doctor.", "zh": "我长大后想当医生。"},
