        {"en": "Excuse me, how can I get to the hospital?", "zh": "打扰一下, 我怎么去医院?"},
        {"en": "Go straight and turn left at the crossing.", "zh": "直走，在十字路口左转。"},
        {"en": "The bank is next to the supermarket.", "zh": "银行在超市旁边。"},
        {"en": "The park is opposite the school.", "zh": "公园在学校对面。"},
        {"en": "It's between the bookshop and the cinema.", "zh": "它在书店和电影院之间。"},
        {"en": "You can see it on your right.", "zh": "你能在右边看到它。"},
        {"en": "Go along this road for two blocks.", "zh": "沿着这条路走两个街区。"},
        {"en": "Turn right at the traffic light.", "zh": "在红绿灯处右转。"},
        {"en": "The library is behind the hospital.", "zh": "图书馆在医院后面。"},
